Mirror art is a decorative wall mirror designed to improve the beauty of a space while also being functional. It is more stylish than a regular mirror and is used to give rooms a modern, elegant, and luxurious look. Mirror art comes in many styles such as round mirrors, geometric mirrors, framed mirrors, sunburst designs, floral patterns, and modern abstract shapes. Mirrors can also make a room feel brighter and larger by reflecting light.

Common Prices of Mirror Art (Pakistan)

Prices depend on size, frame material, and design:

Small mirror art: PKR 3,000 – 7,000
Medium mirror art: PKR 7,000 – 15,000
Large / premium mirror art: PKR 15,000+
Where It Is Used
Living room wall
Above sofa
Bedroom wall
Dressing area
Hallway / entrance
Office reception